At first listen I could only identify one of them with certainity: Track no. 7 is "Theme from Grea Cities" by Simple Minds. You can find it on the album "Sons and Fascination"....

I KNOW that I have track no. 5 somewhere, I thought it was Dead Can dance, but the song wasn't to be found on any of my albums. At least the vocalist sound like Brandon Perry
Found it: No. 5 is "ullysses" from the album "Serpents egg"
No 11. is "Haiti" by Cabaret Voltaire from the album The Crackdown
As mentioned by others here: No. 10 is "Perfect" by The The in 12' version. It can be found on the collection 45 RPM in original and 12' version. Song appeared originally on the album "Soul Mining"
